          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1714734049225-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then add your <strong>green beans</strong> to a pot and cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> (just enough to cover them) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p><p>Once tender, drain and return to the pot with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – these are your <strong>buttered green beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
